{"tid":2169063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"阻紀念7.21  百警闖商場票控犯聚","createTime":"2020-08-22T07:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T09:08:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d56f5bf254140b87e68f45da7796dc6b64f8b1f7","tid":2169063,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T07:56:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/SYOCTXPFEZH3DNQ57X2JIQRW6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FSYOCTXPFEZH3DNQ57X2JIQRW6I%2F&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6corGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=284d522f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200822%2FSYOCTXPFEZH3DNQ57X2JIQRW6I%2F&h=da6e23cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200822/SYOCTXPFEZH3DNQ57X2JIQRW6I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n阻紀念7.21  百警闖商場票控犯聚<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日是7.21元朗恐襲第13個月，市民毋忘港殤，發起「和你lunch」活動，晚上亦有市民到Yoho Mall聚集紀念，不過去年「唔見人」的警方卻重兵部署，傍晚起有過百警力駐守元朗西鐵站，其後大批防暴警闖入商場截查數十名市民，再以違反限聚令票控，引起不滿。對前日警方高調再拘捕六名涉案白衣人，但昨有五人獲釋，不少市民直斥警方當晚不保護市民已盡失民心，事隔近400日只拘捕43人，包括當日打人的瓜農陳志祥及主腦等仍逍遙法外，部份更潛逃外地，坦言對警方執法不抱期望。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/m6bb-lpZ8CRoaah_KlzOdjKZqRs=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GAYA4QP2KJCSNMQZAHTD75KY7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fm6bb-lpZ8CRoaah_KlzOdjKZqRs%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGAYA4QP2KJCSNMQZAHTD75KY7U.jpg&h=d068bc44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■昨晚近百防暴警闖入元朗Yoho Mall，設起封鎖線截查市民。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n柳俊江諷警執法「講就兇狠」<br />\n<br />\n警方前日在7.21元朗恐襲第13個月的前夕，高調公佈再拘捕六人，是去年11月以來警方就7.21事件再拘捕涉案人士，令案中。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n對警方揚言無論兇徒「匿到天腳底」，「一定拉佢返嚟」，7.21恐襲中遇。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n昨午有網民發起到南邊圍村「和你lunch」，中午起數十防暴警在事發當晚有大批白衣人集結的南邊圍佈防，被諷「39分鐘sir」的新界北總區指揮官曾正科亦在場，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至晚上8時，大批防暴警在元朗西鐵站佈防，當時並無市民聚集，其後有市民在元朗Yoho Mall一期聚集貼文宣，高叫「7.21唔見人」等口號，又舉起五一手勢。其。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1XSbEzGLnHqvOEvu8Zl0AXXnCoE=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TEM7M3Y6OFAPTBYGZ5MH3APKGQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1XSbEzGLnHqvOEvu8Zl0AXXnCoE%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTEM7M3Y6OFAPTBYGZ5MH3APKGQ.jpg&h=5fc90016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳先生指自己路過卻被警員票控，表明不會交罰款。"},{"pid":"198d1465776f3c44ef37545d8e0522a9ea2c3b6f","tid":2169063,"uid":367280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T08:49:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dd76bb6b0d941c26491016c3900e670d76ff9c02","tid":2169063,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"831點算？"},{"pid":"a98d0bff471f590ef1ce18411161919c996beb85","tid":2169063,"uid":161711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd76bb6b0d941c26491016c3900e670d76ff9c02","tid":2169063,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"831點算？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T09:08:36.000Z","msg":"成條彌敦道票控"}]}